spec_data.Name: btrbk
spec_data.Description:
Backup tool for btrfs sub-volumes, using a configuration file, allows
creation of backups from multiple sources to multiple destinations,
with ssh and flexible retention policy support (hourly, daily,
weekly, monthly)
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Wed 04 Oct 2017 03:46:54 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Tool for creating snapshots and remote backups of btrfs sub-volumes
